This button adds new images to the Custom Buttons Editor and is based on a button of the same name that can be found in the [url=https://forum.mozilla-russia.org/viewtopic.php?id=55963]Mozilla Russian forum[/url]. The author is [b]SendAbuse[/b] and is based on an idea by [b]okkamas_knife[/b] with code contribution from [b]InfoCatcher[/b].

The main difference between my version of this button compared to the original, is that I have added the option to add images from a folder. I also added a menu to change certain options.

